  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the project is to improve the overall treatment and outcome of renal, pancreas or
      liver transplanted patients who have encountered a malignancy by a structured treatment
      program for diagnosis and treatment of the malignancy, optimization of the immunosuppressive
      treatment, follow-up and evaluation of the program.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
